- **Material Type:** The market can be segmented by material type, such as low-density polyethylene (LDPE), linear low-density polyethylene (LLDPE), high-density polyethylene (HDPE), ethylene vinyl acetate (EVA), and others. The choice of material impacts film durability, flexibility, and thermal properties.
